import * as React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import classnames from 'classnames' import { asCurrency } from '../../utils/number' import styles from './styles.module.css' function Listing({ listing }) { if (!listing) { return null } const { id, image, title, address, description, price } = listing const cardClasses = classnames('card', styles.card) return (
{title}
CAD {asCurrency(price.value)}
{address}
{description}
Details
) } export default Listing
